Rebuild /System/Links directories.

Usage: RebuildLinks <option>

Options:
* '''-h, --help''' - Shows this help.
* '''-v, --version''' - Show program version.
* '''-V, --verbose''' - Enable verbose mode.
* '''-s, --shared''' - Rebuild /System/Links/Shared.
* '''-n, --environment''' - Rebuild /System/Links/Environment.

Not all directories in the /System/Links hierarchy can be rebuilt using this tool because it would render the system in an inconsistent state during the program's execution.

Examples:
<blockquote>
RebuildLinks --shared <br/>
</blockquote>

